"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"背景：zklink是一种安全的跨链交换，用硬科学验证 ，由革命性的零知识技术支持的超安全的链到链互操作性协议。\\n\\n![支持者一览](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rG1DF76IHb9d3OLkQdSLw.png?height=373&width=1153)\\n\\n用途: 跨链协议，使得用户资产无缝的在各链上无障碍流动。在已披露的路线图中可得知未来还将支持L2二层协议跨链。目前测试版本中仅支持以太测试网，币安智能链测试，马蹄测试，雪崩测试网。在上一个测试版本中支持HECO TEST（火币生态链）。\\n\\n总结：资产流动性和去中心化协议的重要性不言而喻。优秀的去中心化金融协议也为WEB3.0的早日到达打好根基。\\n\\n开始测试的准备：\\n\\n1\\\\.Zklink测试网站，推特，DISCORD。进入DIS进行钱包绑定认证。\\n\\n[https://zk.link/app/crosschainswap](https://zk.link/app/crosschainswap)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/zkLinkorg](https://twitter.com/zkLinkorg)\\n\\n[https://discord.com/invite/9GCwxN7xaJ](https://discord.com/invite/9GCwxN7xaJ)\\n\\n2\\\\.领水\\n\\nRinkeby Testnet\\nFaucet:\\n<https://faucet.rinkeby.io/>\\nGoerli Testnet\\nFaucet:\\n<https://faucet.goerli.mudit.blog/>\\nFaucet:\\n<https://goerli-faucet.slock.it/>\\nAVAX Testnet\\nRPC URL:\\n<https://api.avax-test.network/ext/bc/C/rpc>\\nChain ID:\\n43113\\nSymbol:\\nAVAX\\nFaucet:\\n<https://faucet.avax-test.network/>\\nPolygon Testnet\\nRPC URL:\\n<https://rpc-mumbai.maticvigil.com>\\nChain ID:\\n80001\\nSymbol:\\nMATIC\\nFaucet:\\n<https://faucet.matic.network/>\\n\\n3\\\\.正式交互\\n\\n![连接钱包，选择Rinkeby网络](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/d3qcnzGK3C9GBHPwJAuHo.png?height=682&width=1366)\\n\\n![领取测试币](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/C9rT6zxWinfLFNfDezbyK.png?height=603&width=576)\\n\\n![选择USDT，点击GET。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/klDb4O-iohUV-kDG_wiTD.png?height=514&width=655)\\n\\n![点击确认](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/KY1EJENmexUjdnwafrG6y.png?height=357&width=959)\\n\\n![提示领取成功](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/TRujDkdu4lX35N5um6A2G.png?height=459&width=940)\\n\\n![领取完测试币后我们选择跨链交互。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kwD8rZOL4jDNHEHT4wNQi.png?height=590&width=1360)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zlGmz4N4G8qgmkWFAg09p.png?height=571&width=553)\\n\\n![选择刚才领取的100个USDT测试币](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2AVw9FfWHFUsIvN_HZbaI.png?height=512&width=467)\\n\\n![由于马蹄链没有流动性，我们选择雪崩测试。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zEtY8Sgp0COG9CGbXuf1v.png?height=534&width=560)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jXK196dcwLl2RfhAqR-Ky.png?height=556&width=483)\\n\\n![如图所示选好网络，选好跨链币种。进行授权。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/prOjVU4_YNLgVzJGvTuJX.png?height=603&width=446)\\n\\n![确认](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fEKewLE2AQWO1IGWSe0pp.png?height=413&width=958)\\n\\n![然后点击跨链。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/IqtliCT-e-DeIP2nKHtZl.png?height=559&width=440)\\n\\n![确认，等待几分钟就会提示成功。其他链的互跨操作同上。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/vXUy00zwDcFUPg0XHdRmD.png?height=540&width=951)\\n\\n![我们回到主页，继续领取L2所需的测试币。](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/PqvSL5yzwmg5RHJRKbBbr.png?height=165&width=911)\\n\\n![选择XNY](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/TMKz5B8Tofo60z-ZHvj1T.png?height=355&width=487)\\n\\n![选择swap](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9rEAQ9gw-p9NoSATJjTmr.png?height=245&width=480)\\n\\n![进行L2存款操作](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/S7fTNPH1WrKdkxxqQkwF6.png?height=596&width=486)\\n\\n![我们选择刚才领好的XNY币](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rM4tAAPJLvpsAY2BKmjgd.png?height=503&width=470)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FbUeyQFFdV9Ej134871CO.png?height=418&width=947)\\n\\n![确认存款](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1YstFELkmo-FC06MQYcdg.png?height=439&width=943)\\n\\n![提示存款成功](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/IpKdao-YbJbfIzJSUYXHS.png?height=573&width=446)\\n\\n这里L2交换没有流动性，等待项目进度，参与下次测试。\\n\\n4\\\\.GALAXY圣诞NFT的要求\\n\\n领取 NFT 链接[https://galaxy.eco/zkLink/campaign/GCTA8UUPRX](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://galaxy.eco/zkLink/campaign/GCTA8UUPRX&sa=D&source=editors&ust=1640583669933601&usg=AOvVaw0CfLlQP4RJ-9KY8y60wnbS)\\n\\n任务内容A. 加入Discord 社区——发布你捕捉快乐时刻的视频、音频或照片——完成后填写表单。\\n\\nDiscord 频道[https://discord.com/invite/9GCwxN7xaJ](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://discord.com/invite/9GCwxN7xaJ&sa=D&source=editors&ust=1640583669934190&usg=AOvVaw2fe_AJNwpvPamP4989NyS4)\\n\\n完成任务填表。[https://forms.gle/zKo4Afp3goqicjfD6](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://forms.gle/zKo4Afp3goqicjfD6&sa=D&source=editors&ust=1640583669934378&usg=AOvVaw3ec85Xwy4ooaP7PF-X5wFe) \\n\\n登录zkLink Test-Beta，完成一笔跨链交换交易。快照每天。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YNZXvPg35rv43xBeeVZxV.png?height=505&width=976)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640763493,\"title\":\"ZKLINK测试网交互+GALAXY圣诞NFT\"},\"digest\":\"wHlPii9JBwEdApRgvZqxHDF7FSyQOdJbhw6feeaixpM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x83E8DF8ddf3cd5b51caFFB337B321467225d4650\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"27aVjXrNVdQvVhDGnuprQVJ1HgSjbKirwClmJ5vUSeM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"knGFBWP7g72RtHVWDxcIbjcdxUfh7484Utvtv7A_SAo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"E_kpQGOD8UBxvaxCkU_G_eixppjqmF943btFDkrEFLMBJ1_QRfvPUz9JbrMg4Rqbgy7iEYa_HznUiFv5U38ZDQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x95536fda2de4cbee2736cbaef0e1d06d63323754005a4ced9c8133f87fa7524670254a3da647d73f22b6e769f2764f51b1c15a573f9d663eff602e03d0bc46461c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"27aVjXrNVdQvVhDGnuprQVJ1HgSjbKirwClmJ5vUSeM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"knGFBWP7g72RtHVWDxcIbjcdxUfh7484Utvtv7A_SAo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"wHlPii9JBwEdApRgvZqxHDF7FSyQOdJbhw6feeaixpM\"}"